<div class="body" id="fhbody-174647894">
	
		
	

	
		
		<div id="text-174647894" class="p">
			
		 	
				According to <a href="https://gs.statcounter.com/os-market-share/desktop/worldwide">Statcounter</a>, Linux use hit another all-time high in July. For July 2024, the statistics website is showing Linux at 4.45%, climbing almost a half a percentage point from June's 4.05% high.
<br> <br>
Is 2024 truly the year of Linux on the desktop?
		 	
		</div>

		

		

		
			
		
	</div>
